# 001 Account Creation

email = olegzaitsevqa@gmail.com
firstName = Oleg
lastName = Zaitsev
password = Qwerty123
dateOfBirth = 26.08.1993

Steps:
1. Open Homepage
2. Click "My Profile" icon
3. Enter valid email into the "Email" field in the "Sign In" pop-up
4. Click the "Continue" button in the "Sign In" pop-up
5. Enter the firstName into the "First Name" field in the "Create Account" pop-up
6. Select the dateOfBirth in the "Date of Birth" field in the "Create Account" pop-up
7. Enter the password into the "Password" field in the "Create Account" pop-up
8. Enter the password into the "Confirm Password" field in the "Create Account" pop-up
9. Check the "Terms & Conditions" checkbox in the "Create Account" pop-up
10. Click the "Create Account" button in the "Create Account" pop-up

Expected result:
1. I see the "Orders" button
2. I see the "Log out" button
3. I see the "Hi + firstName" message

PostConditions:
1. Log out

# 002 Change Account Password

Preconditions:
1. Log in

Steps:
1. Click on the "Account Information" menu item
2. Click the "Change Password" button
3. Enter the Current password into the "Current Password" field
4. Enter the New Password into the "New Password" field
5. Enter the New Password into the "Confirm Password" field
6. Click the "Save" button
7. Log out
8. Log in with new Password

Expected result:
1. I see the "Orders" button
2. I see the "Log out" button
3. I see the "Hi + firstName" message

PostConditions:
1. Log out


# 003 Add Freediving Fins to wishlist

Preconditions:
1. Log in

Steps:
1. Hover over "Products" menu
2. Hover over Freediving -> Freediving Fins
3. Click on the Freediving Fins
4. Click on the "Razor Polygon"
5. CLick on the "Add to Favorites" button
6. Open My Account page
7. Click on the "Wishlist" menu item

Expected result:
1. I see the "You currently have 1 items in your wishlist" message
2. I see the "Remove" button

PostConditions:
1. Remove all goods from wishlist
2. Log out

# 004 Find the product via the Search

Preconditions:
1. Log in

Steps:
1. Click on the Search field
2. Enter the Name of product into the Search field
3. Click the "View all results" button
4. Click the "Filters" button
5. Click the "Clear all"
6. Select the "Orange" color
7. Click the "Show int result" button

Expected result:
1. I see 1 product in the list

PostConditions:
1. Log out

# 005 Delete Account

Preconditions:
1. Log in

Steps:
1. Click on the "Account Information" menu item
2. Click the "Delete my account"
3. Click the "Delete Account" in the "Delete Account" pop-up

Expected result:
1. The User is logged out
2. I see "Sign In" pop-up